query:
SELECT
    MIN (DATE(u.min_time)) AS min_date
FROM
    (
        SELECT
            MIN("timestamp") AS min_time
        FROM
            ais_positions a
        WHERE
            mmsi = $1
        UNION ALL
        SELECT
            MIN("timestamp") AS min_time
        FROM
            vms_positions v
        WHERE
            call_sign = $2
    ) u
